    "asOf": "2021-07-29",
    "date": "2022-10-14T20:39:04Z",
    "text": "Local Infrastructure Funding & Technical Assistance Act or the LIFT Act\n\nThis bill authorizes the Department of Commerce to provide grants under the Public Works and Economic Development Act of 1965 for predevelopment projects\u2014measures required to be completed before construction of resilient climate infrastructure occurs\u2014and related technical assistance. Grants may be provided to economic development districts, states, Indian tribes, local governments, institutions of higher education, individuals, and other organizations as specified by the bill."
